OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779214266
OL,3,CAaron Rai is first Englishman in over
OL,4,Ca century to win golf's PGA
OL,5,CChampionship
OL,7,FAaron Rai has become the first
OL,8,FEnglishman to win golf's PGA
OL,9,FChampionship in more than a century.
OL,11,FThe 31-year-old from Wolverhampton,
OL,12,Fwho had never previously finished in
OL,13,Fthe top 10 at a major, claimed the
OL,14,Ffirst ever title in Pennsylvania
OL,15,Fyesterday.
OL,17,FRai said he owes his first major
OL,18,Fvictory to his wife and parents as he
OL,19,Fstunned the field to win the
OL,20,Fchampionship.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
