PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779214266
OL,3,CAaron Rai is first Englishman in over
OL,4,Ca century to win golf's PGA
OL,5,CChampionship
OL,7,FHe is the first English winner of the
OL,8,Fevent since 1919 and only the fifth
OL,9,FEuropean to win it, fighting off a
OL,10,Fstar-studded field at Aronimink Golf
OL,11,FClub with some exceptional moments to
OL,12,Fshoot a closing 65 and win by three
OL,13,Fshots.
OL,15,FBorn to working-class parents, he
OL,16,Fhailed the sacrifices they made to
OL,17,Fhelp his fledgling career.
OL,19,F"It's probably hard for me to really
OL,20,Fexpress everything that I feel towards
OL,21,Fthem," Rai said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
