PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779214266
OL,3,CAaron Rai is first Englishman in over
OL,4,Ca century to win golf's PGA
OL,5,CChampionship
OL,7,F"I think I'll get way too emotional to
OL,8,Fspeak. My dad was with me every day
OL,9,Fthat I went to practice from the age
OL,10,Fof four, five years old. He actually
OL,11,Fquit his job and started to focus on
OL,12,Fmy golf from a really young age.
OL,14,F"My mum has been absolutely incredible
OL,15,Fas well. She worked extremely long
OL,16,Fhours to just provide for the house
OL,17,Freally. I can't put into words how
OL,18,Fmuch they've done in terms of the
OL,19,Fsupport, in terms of the care, in
OL,20,Fterms of love. I wouldn't be here
OL,21,Fwithout them at all."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
