CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779214266
OL,3,CAaron Rai is first Englishman in over
OL,4,Ca century to win golf's PGA
OL,5,CChampionship
OL,7,FRai is married to fellow professional
OL,8,Fgolfer Gaurika Bishnoi, who plays on
OL,9,Fthe Ladies European Tour.
OL,11,F"I wouldn't be here without her. Both
OL,12,Fas a companion, as a friend, as
OL,13,Fsomeone I'm sharing my life with, but
OL,14,Falso as a real support system for my
OL,15,Fgame," Rai added.
OL,17,F"Her mindset, her advice, her
OL,18,Fthoughts, whether it's technique or
OL,19,Fthe way I'm holding myself is
OL,20,Fabsolutely invaluable."
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@FO]yD@AOU|D@WO]
