OL,3,CAaron Rai is first Englishman in over
OL,4,Ca century to win golf's PGA
OL,5,CChampionship
OL,7,FRai's victory ended America's 10-year
OL,8,Fgrip on the event and he is the first
OL,9,FEnglish winner since the first
OL,10,Fchampion, Jim Barnes.
OL,12,FHis win has earned him more than #2.7
OL,13,Fmillion pounds in prize money.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
